<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 17:29:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国科技工作者因杀害妻子而面临美国指控，家庭暴力和文化分歧成为焦点</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3254807/domestic-abuse-cultural-divide-spotlight-chinese-tech-worker-faces-us-charges-wifes-killing?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>专家表示，配偶暴力在社会或文化上孤立的移民中可能很明显，而且寻求帮助往往会受到耻辱。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 15:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3254807/domestic-abuse-cultural-divide-spotlight-chinese-tech-worker-faces-us-charges-wifes-killing?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车行业如何主导全球市场</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3254708/how-chinas-electric-vehicle-industry-charged-ahead-dominate-global-market?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>过去10年，中国电动汽车保有量已超过2000万辆，但随着优惠政策即将到期，激烈的竞争给汽车制造商的盈利带来压力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 13:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3254708/how-chinas-electric-vehicle-industry-charged-ahead-dominate-global-market?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国就业：高科技驱动下的“两会”推动提高收入和不可或缺的技术工人的社会地位</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3254675/china-jobs-push-raise-incomes-social-standing-indispensable-skilled-workers-two-sessions-amid-hi?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>“两会”代表敦促通过住房和教育方面的改革来改善中国技术工人的地位，因为人才短缺可能会损害其高科技制造业。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 13:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3254675/china-jobs-push-raise-incomes-social-standing-indispensable-skilled-workers-two-sessions-amid-hi?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国瞄准高科技和私营部门以推动创造就业机会</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3254806/china-targets-hi-tech-and-private-sectors-drive-job-creation?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>人力资源部长表示，结构性问题阻碍了整体就业市场的增长。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 12:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3254806/china-targets-hi-tech-and-private-sectors-drive-job-creation?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国作为世界绿色工厂的崛起让西方陷入了困境</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3254577/chinas-rise-worlds-green-factory-has-put-west-back-foot?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国在太阳能电池板、电动汽车和电池领域日益增长的主导地位使美国和欧洲制造商处于不利地位，并引发了防御性敌意。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 09:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3254577/chinas-rise-worlds-green-factory-has-put-west-back-foot?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>春节消费热潮推动中国消费价格反弹，但通货紧缩风险依然存在</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3254795/chinas-consumer-prices-rebound-thanks-lunar-new-year-spending-boom-deflationary-risks-still-loom?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>2 月份 CPI 同比增长 0.7%，超出预期，标志着连续 6 个月下降后首次上涨，但工厂出厂价格连续第 17 个月下跌，分析师称之为“警告信号”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 07:59:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3254795/chinas-consumer-prices-rebound-thanks-lunar-new-year-spending-boom-deflationary-risks-still-loom?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国债务缠身的贵州在多年来斥资昂贵的项目后面临清算</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254680/chinas-debt-ridden-guizhou-faces-reckoning-after-years-splashing-out-pricey-projects?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国负债最重的省份之一拥有辉煌的桥梁和广阔的道路，但也是全国人均收入水平最差的省份之一，债务压力可能会拖累该地区多年。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 04:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254680/chinas-debt-ridden-guizhou-faces-reckoning-after-years-splashing-out-pricey-projects?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京的军事预算增长速度与去年相同，但台湾不会冒险</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3254627/beijings-military-budget-has-increased-same-rate-last-year-taiwan-taking-no-chances?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>虽然台湾表示不希望与北京进行“军备竞赛”，但它正在采取措施，让军队为潜在的战争做好准备。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 02:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3254627/beijings-military-budget-has-increased-same-rate-last-year-taiwan-taking-no-chances?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院在国会拖延后通过了向太平洋岛国提供的资金</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3254773/us-senate-passes-funds-pacific-island-nations-after-congressional-delays?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>旨在对抗中国在该地区影响力的马绍尔群岛、密克罗尼西亚和帕劳协议作为拨款计划的一部分获得通过。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 01:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3254773/us-senate-passes-funds-pacific-island-nations-after-congressional-delays?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>香港初创企业和投资者在 Leap 2024 为开拓沙特阿拉伯未来的增长奠定基础</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3254762/leap-2024-hong-kong-start-ups-and-investors-lay-groundwork-tap-future-saudi-arabia-growth?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>初创企业和投资者表示，参加 Leap 科技会议是为了为“像 90 年代末的中国”这样的市场建立关系。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 00:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3254762/leap-2024-hong-kong-start-ups-and-investors-lay-groundwork-tap-future-saudi-arabia-growth?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国的支付承诺对游客和外国投资来说是“积极的一步”，但经济和安全问题仍然存在</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3254683/chinas-payment-vow-positive-step-visitors-foreign-investment-economy-and-security-concerns-remain?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国国务院誓言将进一步支持优化支付方式的政策，并承诺为货